<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft, without moulding (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.57</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">1.14</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.56</measure>). The stone is complete; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face.</p>
</div><div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>ll.1-11, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.025</measure>; ll.12 following, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0198" notAfter="0210" exact="both">A.D. 198-210</date>
(Caracalla's <rs type="criteria">reign</rs>)</p>
</div>
